  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stop, turn, and go all out toward the destination! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One collision and the game’s over!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/481688b7355ef3d71453dac6d02e5171.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is Pocket & Zooom?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pocket & Zooom is a puzzle game in which you give commands to aircraft to guide them to their destinations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can give only six kinds of commands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's more difficult than it sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a strategy to get the aircraft to their destinations!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to play Pocket & Zooom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Always keep your eye on the airport!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aircraft move steadily towards their destinations, but without your guidance they can easily collide with other aircraft or obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep a close eye on conditions at the airport, quickly find aircraft that are heading into dangerous situations and avoid the danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Give commands to the aircraft!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use \"command cards\" to keep the aircraft away from danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the appropriate command from six command cards, including \"Stop\" and \"Change Route,\" to guide the aircraft to their destinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Be careful not to use too many cards!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After using a card, there is a “cooldown” time during which you have to wait before you can use another card. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think carefully about timing when you use a card.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>[Guide all the aircraft to their destinations!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Safely avoid various dangers and get the aircraft to their destinations to be a hero!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you only had to guide one aircraft it might be easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But with each new stage, the number of aircraft increases and the dangers become more frequent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide all the aircraft to their destinations to clear the stage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stop, turn, and go all out toward the destination! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One collision and the game’s over!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/481688b7355ef3d71453dac6d02e5171.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is Pocket & Zooom?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pocket & Zooom is a puzzle game in which you give commands to aircraft to guide them to their destinations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can give only six kinds of commands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's more difficult than it sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a strategy to get the aircraft to their destinations!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to play Pocket & Zooom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Always keep your eye on the airport!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aircraft move steadily towards their destinations, but without your guidance they can easily collide with other aircraft or obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep a close eye on conditions at the airport, quickly find aircraft that are heading into dangerous situations and avoid the danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Give commands to the aircraft!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use \"command cards\" to keep the aircraft away from danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the appropriate command from six command cards, including \"Stop\" and \"Change Route,\" to guide the aircraft to their destinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Be careful not to use too many cards!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After using a card, there is a “cooldown” time during which you have to wait before you can use another card. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think carefully about timing when you use a card.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>[Guide all the aircraft to their destinations!]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Safely avoid various dangers and get the aircraft to their destinations to be a hero!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you only had to guide one aircraft it might be easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But with each new stage, the number of aircraft increases and the dangers become more frequent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide all the aircraft to their destinations to clear the stage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.poster.avif?t=1773892966\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.webm?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.mp4?t=1773892966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
